summary: Opening commissions!!! Heyo!! I am broke and currently have no income to pay for stuff. If you’re interested in making a...
caption:
Opening commissions!!!

Heyo!! I am broke and currently have no income to pay for stuff. If you’re interested in making a purchase send a DM my way and I’ll get you set up! P.S. This is my first time working on commissions so be gentle, pls and ty. (´･ω･`)

  • Payment will be through paypal. My email is lamarian@hotmail.com
  • You will need to tell me which commission type you want, specific poses and color palettes, ect
  • Visual reference/s for OCs would be appreciated. An additional 25% fee will be required without one.
  • Character descriptions are welcome and appreciated!! Let me know all about your character so I can have a better understanding on how I should draw them.
  • I will start drawing once it’s paid. It shouldn’t take me more than two weeks to complete.


  • Things I draw are; furries, humanoids, fanart, OCs, gore
  • Things I won’t draw; NSFW, mecha, IRL ships, backgrounds, extreme gore, complex characters

SLOTS

  1. OPEN
  2. OPEN
  3. OPEN
  4. OPEN
  5. OPEN

✧･ﾟ: *✧･ﾟ:* Reblogs are loved and welcomed!!  *:･ﾟ✧*:･ﾟ✧

blog.title: I Am Braveheartcatlover
blog.description:
I'm a relaxed awesome woman who enjoys drawing, writing, poetry, and cute, fluffy things.
"Inside each and every one of you, there is a fire. No matter how tiny or how dim you think it is, there is a fire. You just need to find the ones to help ignite the flame,"-me

summary: While I am working on my story, I am going to be drawing some Warrior cats. I love Squirrelflight. When she first appeared in...
caption: While I am working on my story, I am going to be drawing some Warrior cats. I love Squirrelflight. When she first appeared in the book, she annoyed me a fair bit. But as time when on she slowly grew on me. I feel like she was a very good mother, even to kits that were not technically hers. She has a very big heart and I personality think that her and Bramblestar are a cute couple.
